<span style=\"color: red;\">林志偉亦稱，如果在其他國家和地區，警方可能會使用武力程度更高的措施，但香港警方只使用最低的武力去應對，全世界有理性的人都能明白警方的專業水平。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2208881/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2208881%2F&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=0739ac5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2208881/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"【極重要】其實已經拉左一百個人！我係前線手足，我有野想講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395864</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9iKJ6yN_ehM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9iKJ6yN_ehM&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=eb942678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9iKJ6yN_ehM</a>"},{"pid":"305d3d64e50d2fe3a9dee3307e451a38478e8e98","tid":1396844,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68afd15a0de776b98589443a9f23209c2ccd3d74","tid":1396844,"uid":19698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"交換"},{"pid":"2250e8ebd5a5b27d523c232ad9b8b55d428b0de2","tid":1396844,"uid":97871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"下下都出子彈 低你老母咩"},{"pid":"f38b6252679c62bae1a80e134a18da465c6f8d8c","tid":1396844,"uid":214124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"即刻同我入黎 唔準當義士condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1aefb4fa7f5ce9a5e9c983aa799bf1ab665bc5bb","tid":1396844,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"有冇搞撚錯呀林志偉！你班咁嘅陷家剷舊電池過氣油炸鬼仲死撚出黎做乜鳩呀吓！司法公義關你鳩事咩?你地都果頭近行將就木聞見棺材香過飯！<br />\n咩呀?係咪份糧唔撚夠洗呀出黎讉責?即係咩呀話比人聽老而不廢呀?<br />\n鳩毛都就黎甩撚晒喇因住中風呀爆血管呀！洗唔撚洗CALL定黑白車比你呀?<br />\n屌你老母你班陷家剷燈膽都燒撚埋漏撚晒氣仲走出黎說三道四指手劃腳?<br />\n你估你地冇砌過生豬肉呀！想垂簾聽政?點解唔撚上禮賓府呀唔撚夠氣呀定老人痴呆唔撚識路呀?咁撚得閒就不如去行下寶福山喇搵返個靚位比自己仲好喇！！<br />\n屌你老母司法公義留撚返同閻羅王講留撚返同牛頭馬面講喇！<br />\n老散都咁撚多事幹指手劃腳?我呀，睇新聞都見到好多退休沙展幾撚悽涼臨老唔撚得過世，屌你老母生仔冇屎忽唔撚係吞槍就跳樓皆因後生果陣砌得生豬肉多呀。差佬呀幾撚時同市民講過司法公義呀吓！<br />\n讉責? 讉你媽個閪呀！讉?<br />\n邊撚個比飯你食呀飲水思源好喎！你地有乜撚野資格講司法公義呀?80年代又唔撚見你地出黎講?<br />\n唔撚想生仔冇屎忽第時退休就嘔撚返晒D退休金出黎！<br />\n等你百年歸老我地一人捐一個大餅出黎比你掟口<br />\n掟撚埋你個屎眼！<br />\n掟撚埋你個仔個屎眼！！(有嘅話)"},{"pid":"183c73c42a7cbcbbf143090c2d7da9b5979a4ca9","tid":1396844,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"位唔係咁上 而家成個警隊陪撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f4020fb00bffc4936dcdae8f57b450d87f2ced","tid":1396844,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"祝陷家剷全家死絕一口不留"},{"pid":"2480f83592970fe8951918cc1417762144738102","tid":1396844,"uid":55646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"林志偉特首正式上線啦"},{"pid":"e742dc02b298a27f8187002faea3809cb449f8e4","tid":1396844,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc215b8e8a5377b6554c9d1e97d77f4c4badceb7","tid":1396844,"uid":155789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"佢其實守緊邊個警區"},{"pid":"3cb31b12263d8182d0d79ff57607cd86cf493a07","tid":1396844,"uid":281533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"c12d278a6ead66d3bc223a2e445bb04fbc26a1ce","tid":1396844,